588
00:40:36,308 --> 00:40:38,060
And, Sir.

589
00:40:38,602 --> 00:40:42,064
Do you have an extra work uniform?

590
00:40:49,238 --> 00:40:50,239
Everyone.

591
00:40:51,323 --> 00:40:54,785
I'm well aware that you're all
