00:45:10,249 --> 00:45:11,083
Yeah.

654
00:45:11,500 --> 00:45:13,836
That's under Jae-seok's name, isn't it?

655
00:45:14,336 --> 00:45:15,170
Yeah.

656
00:45:15,629 --> 00:45:18,090
