660
00:45:37,526 --> 00:45:39,903
I was very impressed with
your press conference last time.

661
00:45:41,405 --> 00:45:42,364
Were you?

662
00:45:42,448 --> 00:45:44,199
You're having a hard time
in many ways, aren't you?

